channel.title: Comments on: Rare Weezer falls out of black hole

item.title: By: cal
item.dc:creator: cal
item.description: sharpless is almost correct. much of the list above is BS. but Superfriend and O Jonas are in fact from SFTBH. The reason O Jonas "sounds nothing like Rivers" is because... duh... it isn't. It's the female role of the opera (Maria), sung by Joan Wasser.
item.content:encoded: sharpless is almost correct. much of the list above is BS. but Superfriend and O Jonas are in fact from SFTBH. The reason O Jonas “sounds nothing like Rivers” is because… duh… it isn’t. It’s the female role of the opera (Maria), sung by Joan Wasser.
